casebody.data:
Lynda LIKE, et al., petitioners,
v.
TRANSCONTINENTAL GAS PIPE LINE COMPANY, LLC. No. 18-1206. Supreme Court of the United States May 28, 2019.

Motion of owners' Counsel of America, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit denied.
